replies.bodyText:
Also the full thing can be re-written as:
Optional.ofNullable(role.getPrivileges())
			.map(p -> p.stream().filter(pr -> !Context.hasPrivilege(pr.getPrivilege())).map(Privilege::getPrivilege)
				.distinct().collect(Collectors.joining(", ")))
				.ifPresent(missing -> {
					throw new APIException("Role.you.must.have.privileges: ", new Object[] { missing });
				});
Which is preferable since we only have one call to Collectors and one call to stream() (in the streaming API, these are the expensive operations which actual result in computation being done).

